{"tid":1715030,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[行動post]仲番緊工既你！幫手宣傳無限期三罷","createTime":"2019-11-13T03:55:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T04:14:21.000Z","uid":89974,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4c8dd85bc8f9f5c2d3835c94d0111c5e451eeb14","tid":1715030,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T03:55:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">前言：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n以下係對所有<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">好心痛，但仲番緊工，唔敢罷工，剩係碌手機睇新聞既人</span></span>講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">碌手機睇新聞係無用架！我地要做實事！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">分析：</span></span><br />\n中大係士氣之爭，係對錯之爭，係信念之爭。<br />\n但無限期三罷係<strong>勝負手</strong>！<br />\n呢幾日既大罷工社會癱瘓係因為我地犧牲咗唔少手足換番嚟！每日都有人俾曱甴拉！<br />\n換嚟更多時間俾我地宣傳同下決心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家最緊要係<span style=\"color: red;\">大量大量大量既宣傳</span>，將港豬淺黃深黃拉哂入罷工channel到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尤其是仲係office涼冷氣個班，手足捱子彈你好意思仲番工做野咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無限期三罷最大既問題一直都在於囚徒困境，而我地已經有手足搞緊工會同基金去為大家免除後顧之憂！就算未成立得切工會同基金，<strong>只要我地聚得足夠多人，最後一樣能夠直接罷工癱瘓香港！</strong> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">點做：</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1.係Facebook, Whatsapp, IG狂炸呢幾張相俾朋友同公海group！</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7rJDr4v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7rJDr4v.jpg&h=1696faf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UiwYr4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUiwYr4w.jpg&h=0ba516b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ouDjVXR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FouDjVXR.jpg&h=c3b1e379&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VcVRM4x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVcVRM4x.jpg&h=adf68e81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2.加入罷工頻道，幫手組織工會！</span><br />\n <a href=\"http://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLad5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=f9ac597a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkonstrike</a> &lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;即時加入<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3.IG, Whatsapp, Facebook<span style=\"color: red;\">換頭像</span>顯示你會罷工既決心兼share呢個post！</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2RD0Fpd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2RD0Fpd.jpg&h=5a796b1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/BRAVEHONGKONG/photos/147268086626134/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FBRAVEHONGKONG%2Fphotos%2F147268086626134%2F&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLad5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=78bc7da5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/BRAVEHONGKONG/photos/147268086626134/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港抗爭已經進入到另一個階段，好多和理非規則已經不再有效。<br />\n唔好再欺騙自己仲可以平靜生活，屠殺來臨時無一倖免。<br />\n而家係生死之戰，香港已經係戰場。</span></span>"},{"pid":"4f58397f5d6cb4d30b775dc97069af7c1bb35d6c","tid":1715030,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T03:57:38.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"efd7a6c6c0bd6455c892bbbfed3761ce23d11e69","tid":1715030,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T03:58:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3144cc74d920d706ab19a92339d625354065f089","tid":1715030,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T03:58:1